        <h2>Want to know more?</h2>
        <p>This Arthub page is a temporary window pending the development of an integration of the collection in <a href="https://www.museabrugge.be">www.museabrugge.be</a>. Behind this generic window is a completely new groundwork provided by the <a href="https://www.vlaamsekunstcollectie.be">Flemish Art Collection</a> (VKC). The VKC ecosystem combines the metadata or data from Adlib with the images from a new DAM system (ResourceSpace), hosted by MeeMoo. The use of high-resolution images through the use of IIIF allows for the disclosure of online images and to make details of images and metadata accessible. In addition, it is possible to add shared annotations and enable reuse. As an internal functionality, this makes it possible, for example, to apply condition reports directly to the image itself. Finally, screening and analysis of the metadata will be possible via a Dashboard of Musea Brugge.</p>

        <p>This project was realized in collaboration with the <a href="https://www.vlaamsekunstcollectie.be">Flemish Art Collection</a> thanks to a project subsidy from the Flemish Government.</p>
